01:23:39.502 --> 01:23:41.367
Oh. Hello.

01:23:42.238 --> 01:23:43.364
I'm surprised to see you.

01:23:46.842 --> 01:23:50.278
As am I to see you.
I didn't think you liked parties.

01:23:50.546 --> 01:23:53.310
Gabriella insisted
I come and she's an old friend.

01:23:55.251 --> 01:23:58.186
You know that Cristina and
I are no longer together, right?

01:23:58.321 --> 01:23:59.253
Yes.

01:24:00.222 --> 01:24:02.281
So now you're
just with your ex-wife?

01:24:02.858 --> 01:24:04.382
No, Maria Elena is gone as well.

01:24:05.795 --> 01:24:06.591
For now.

01:24:07.997 --> 01:24:10.329
It's funny. Maria Elena and I...

01:24:11.233 --> 01:24:13.599
...are meant for each other and
not meant for each other.

01:24:14.937 --> 01:24:15.869
It's a contradiction.

01:24:16.339 --> 01:24:19.775
In order to understand it,
you need a poet, like my father.

01:24:20.810 --> 01:24:21.834
Because I don't.

01:24:26.215 --> 01:24:27.113
How about you?

01:24:27.516 --> 01:24:29.279
All goes well with your husband?

01:24:29.418 --> 01:24:31.943
Oh, yes, he's wonderful.

01:24:32.254 --> 01:24:33.084
He's terrific.

01:24:33.222 --> 01:24:36.248
I'm quite delighted with
the way things turned out.

01:24:37.560 --> 01:24:38.822
Why don't I believe you?

01:24:41.130 --> 01:24:44.190
Don't become flirtatious.

01:24:45.067 --> 01:24:47.331
I realize your bed is empty now...

01:24:47.470 --> 01:24:49.597
...and you always had
a little yen for me,

01:24:49.739 --> 01:24:52.367
but we're preparing to leave
by the weekend, so...

01:24:52.508 --> 01:24:53.736
Meet me for lunch.

01:24:56.979 --> 01:24:59.345
I'm too scared.

01:25:03.019 --> 01:25:03.815
What?

01:25:04.587 --> 01:25:06.612
You're breaking up, Tom.

01:25:07.423 --> 01:25:08.481
You're breaking up.

01:25:09.425 --> 01:25:10.289
Where are you?

01:25:11.694 --> 01:25:13.025
Okay. That's better.

01:25:13.295 --> 01:25:13.818
That's better.

01:25:13.963 --> 01:25:15.453
Just try to stand still.

01:25:16.732 --> 01:25:17.892
Can you hear me?

01:25:18.567 --> 01:25:22.059
We have to get
a bird for Mark and Judy.

01:25:22.304 --> 01:25:23.771
No. We can't get them a bird.

01:25:23.906 --> 01:25:25.134
- Why not?
- It's ridiculous.

01:25:25.274 --> 01:25:26.172
They're beautiful.

01:25:26.275 --> 01:25:27.867
I always wanted a bird.

01:25:28.010 --> 01:25:29.307
You know, when we get home,

01:25:29.445 --> 01:25:32.107
I'd love to get a bird
for the new house.

01:25:32.648 --> 01:25:33.342
Yeah?

01:25:33.482 --> 01:25:36.883
Yeah. And I'm leaning towards
Bedford Hills.

01:25:37.086 --> 01:25:37.677
What do you think?

01:25:37.820 --> 01:25:39.310
Yeah, yeah.

01:25:40.189 --> 01:25:40.917
Hold on.

01:25:43.125 --> 01:25:43.819
Hello.

01:25:44.326 --> 01:25:46.123
Spend tomorrow afternoon with me.

01:25:48.164 --> 01:25:49.153
No. It's not possible.

01:25:49.298 --> 01:25:51.732
We're preparing to
leave by the weekend.

01:25:52.134 --> 01:25:55.626
Be on the corner of
Calle Tiles in Pedralbes.

01:25:55.771 --> 01:25:58.899
And... I'll drive by and pick
you up at noon.

01:26:00.443 --> 01:26:02.638
No. I... You're wasting your time.

01:26:02.778 --> 01:26:03.904
I can't talk now.

01:26:04.613 --> 01:26:06.513
Look... I'm not the kind of man

01:26:06.649 --> 01:26:10.107
who would try to come between
a husband and wife. I'm not...

01:26:10.252 --> 01:26:13.949
But Judy Nash called me
and tells me you are not happy.

01:26:14.256 --> 01:26:17.623
That you are actually more in love
with me than the man you married.

01:26:18.694 --> 01:26:19.422
I can't talk.

01:26:32.274 --> 01:26:34.367
Hey, babe. What do you think?

01:26:35.544 --> 01:26:36.374
Who was that?

01:26:37.613 --> 01:26:38.514
On the phone.

01:26:38.514 --> 01:26:41.847
Oh, it was my, uh, language teacher.

01:26:45.254 --> 01:26:45.777
He wants me to have

01:26:45.921 --> 01:26:48.481
a good-bye lunch with
him tomorrow at noon.

01:26:49.592 --> 01:26:50.058
That's perfect.

01:26:50.192 --> 01:26:52.353
I'm going to play golf with
Mark in the morning.

01:28:03.199 --> 01:28:04.291
Well, this is...

01:28:07.303 --> 01:28:09.828
I've been working
on these ones lately.

01:28:14.443 --> 01:28:16.070
They're very overwhelming. Oh, my God.

01:28:17.546 --> 01:28:19.537
It's very hard to explain a painting.

01:28:19.682 --> 01:28:22.674
You don't have to. It's fascinating.

01:28:22.818 --> 01:28:26.254
This one, actually,
should be the other way around.

01:28:29.792 --> 01:28:31.623
No, I like it very much.

01:28:31.927 --> 01:28:35.192
Can I...
can I be frank about something?

01:28:35.331 --> 01:28:35.820
Yeah.

01:28:35.965 --> 01:28:39.128
This one. It's...

01:28:39.368 --> 01:28:41.529
There's something
very frightening about it.

01:28:42.738 --> 01:28:43.898
That one is Maria Elena's.

01:28:44.039 --> 01:28:47.065
Well, that explains it.
It's very chaotic.

01:28:48.143 --> 01:28:50.805
Erratic, almost. But...

01:28:51.447 --> 01:28:53.608
Oh, God, what am I doing here?

01:28:54.183 --> 01:28:56.151
I don't know what I expect to happen.

01:28:56.552 --> 01:29:00.454
It's been a long time since
we made love that night in Oviedo.

01:29:01.156 --> 01:29:03.147
I've thought about it many, many times.

01:29:03.292 --> 01:29:04.281
I'm sure you weren't thinking about it

01:29:04.426 --> 01:29:07.623
when you were making love to
Cristina or Maria Elena.

01:29:07.763 --> 01:29:09.321
Well, I never lied to you.

01:29:09.465 --> 01:29:11.524
I told you from the first moment

01:29:11.667 --> 01:29:13.726
that I was attracted to
both you and Cristina.

01:29:13.869 --> 01:29:20.433
I, I can't just go to bed with you.
I'm... I'm not good at this.

01:29:20.609 --> 01:29:23.476
- But you weren't nervous that night.
- I wasn't married.

01:29:23.679 --> 01:29:24.839
You were about to be.

01:29:25.014 --> 01:29:27.482
Yeah, you're right.
It's what I want.

01:29:27.750 --> 01:29:29.650
But what am I supposed to do?

01:29:29.752 --> 01:29:31.617
Make love with you and then go

01:29:31.754 --> 01:29:33.984
on with my marriage
like nothing happened?

01:29:34.123 --> 01:29:35.818
Or, just terminate it?

01:29:35.958 --> 01:29:38.722
Judy Nash says you are heading
for an unhappy life.

01:29:38.861 --> 01:29:41.455
Yeah, well, she's talking
about herself.

01:29:42.531 --> 01:29:44.089
Maybe you will understand

01:29:44.233 --> 01:29:46.428
more about your own feelings
once we've made love.

01:29:46.568 --> 01:29:47.762
Yeah, or less.

01:29:47.903 --> 01:29:50.269
Look, I'm not saying
I'm not tempted...

01:29:50.406 --> 01:29:54.274
...but it would require
such an upheaval, emotionally...

01:29:54.410 --> 01:29:57.504
and from a practical point of view,
you're not exactly the kind of man

01:29:57.646 --> 01:29:59.546
to plan a future with.

01:30:04.520 --> 01:30:05.714
What are you doing?!

01:30:06.522 --> 01:30:07.648
You're goin' to kill yourself!

01:30:08.090 --> 01:30:09.421
I don't want to live.

01:30:09.558 --> 01:30:16.361
I don't want to live, damn it!

01:30:16.932 --> 01:30:17.830
Let it go. Now, now, now.

01:30:25.441 --> 01:30:29.207
Don't you understand that
I don't want to live,

01:30:29.345 --> 01:30:34.044
that I can't live like this.
My head is going to explode.

01:30:34.183 --> 01:30:35.480
I can't take this anymore.

01:30:35.617 --> 01:30:37.278
I can't take it anymore.

01:30:38.587 --> 01:30:39.849
Give me the gun.

01:30:39.988 --> 01:30:43.947
Give me the gun. Damn it!

01:30:44.093 --> 01:30:46.789
Listen to me, please, my love.

01:30:47.229 --> 01:30:48.526
My love, listen to me.

01:30:49.164 --> 01:30:50.756
Come. Give me your hand.

01:30:51.400 --> 01:30:55.302
Come. It's okay.
It's okay, my love. It's okay.

01:30:57.139 --> 01:30:57.764
Oh, my God.

01:30:57.906 --> 01:30:59.533
Oh, my God, I'm so sorry!

01:31:02.945 --> 01:31:04.537
Oh, my God, you're both crazy!

01:31:04.680 --> 01:31:08.047
Both of you are completely insane!

01:31:08.183 --> 01:31:10.310
How the hell am I going to
explain this to my husband?!

01:31:10.452 --> 01:31:12.249
I can't live like this!

01:31:12.388 --> 01:31:14.151
This is not my life!

01:31:14.289 --> 01:31:16.757
I just can't do it!

01:31:20.696 --> 01:31:23.665
I still don't understand
why your language teacher had a gun.

01:31:23.799 --> 01:31:24.356
I told you.

01:31:24.500 --> 01:31:26.525
He collects antique firearms.

01:31:26.668 --> 01:31:29.102
- He was showing me his favorite one
- God! We should sue him!

01:31:29.238 --> 01:31:31.138
- and it went off.
- That is so irresponsible!

01:31:31.273 --> 01:31:34.265
No, it's not that bad, honestly.

01:31:34.410 --> 01:31:35.809
What if something happened to you?

01:31:36.378 --> 01:31:38.471
What? What are you saying?

01:31:39.047 --> 01:31:40.378
I love you so much.

01:31:41.283 --> 01:31:43.478
Doug never found out the real story.

01:31:46.422 --> 01:31:48.515
Judy knew the secret and,
of course, was relieved

01:31:48.657 --> 01:31:51.148
that Vicky had not been hurt worse,
or killed.

01:31:52.494 --> 01:31:54.257
With Vicky leaving to
go back to New York,

01:31:54.496 --> 01:31:55.929
Judy's plans to rescue Vicky...

01:31:56.064 --> 01:31:58.658
...from her own fate were
put on terminal hold.

01:32:02.538 --> 01:32:05.871
When Cristina returned from Antibes,
Vicky told her the whole tale...

01:32:06.175 --> 01:32:07.403
and Cristina thought it was sad

01:32:07.543 --> 01:32:09.374
how much Vicky
had wanted Juan Antonio...

01:32:09.578 --> 01:32:11.910
...and was unable to say or
do anything about it.

01:32:12.214 --> 01:32:13.613
I would have stepped aside.

01:32:13.749 --> 01:32:15.580
Look, I knew you had feelings

01:32:15.717 --> 01:32:18.743
for Juan Antonio
the moment you saw him.

01:32:18.921 --> 01:32:21.219
But if I knew what had happened,
I never would have gone ahead with it.

01:32:21.356 --> 01:32:22.880
Look, it was a...

01:32:23.859 --> 01:32:25.656
...a passing thing.

01:32:27.329 --> 01:32:28.318
Now it's over.

01:32:56.725 --> 01:32:59.285
Vicky went home to have her
grand wedding to Doug...

01:32:59.928 --> 01:33:02.021
...to the house they both
finally settled on...

01:33:02.264 --> 01:33:03.959
...and to lead the life
she had envisioned

01:33:04.099 --> 01:33:06.829
for herself before the
summer in Barcelona.

01:33:08.070 --> 01:33:10.038
Cristina continued searching...

01:33:10.772 --> 01:33:13.502
...certain only of
what she didn't want.

